			<th bgcolor="#d8dde4" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol0 twikiFirstCol twikiLast"> <font color="#252b37">bdii_servers</font> </th>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol1 twikiLast"> String </td>
			<td bgcolor="#f2f3f6" valign="top" class="twikiTableCol2 twikiLastCol twikiLast"> This should be set to the BDII servers that the installation should report information to.  This should be formatted as server_url[FORMAT],server_url2[FORMAT] where FORMAT is the CEMon format to use for reporting.  The format is RAW for most BDII servers. E.g. for production resources this might be <code>http://is1.grid.iu.edu:14001[RAW]</code>, <code>http://is2.grid.iu.edu:14001[RAW]</code> </td>
		</tr></table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr class="twikinetWrapperTableRow">
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableB twikinetWrapperTableBL"></td>
<td class="twikinetWrapperTableB twikinetWrapperTableBR"></td>
</tr>
